<p><a name="Examples" id="Examples"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Binaural_recording&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Examples">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Examples</span></h2>
